<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/sysml#indicatesRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/sysml#indicatesRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq#ProgramRisk> .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/sysml#indicatesRisk> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Relates a process, such as a failed verification, to the program risk (a disposition) whose presence it indicates. Deliberately NOT BFO 'realizes' (obo:BFO_0000055): a failed test EVIDENCES the risk disposition; it does not realize it -- the risk is realized by the later undesired programmatic process." .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/sysml#indicatesRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/sysml> .
