<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/horizon#LegislativeCandidateChange> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A descriptive information content entity that DESCRIBES a proposed, not-yet-in-effect change to the defense acquisition system, extracted from a specific legislative instrument. EPISTEMIC DISCIPLINE: asserting an instance of this class asserts ONLY that the proposal exists and what it describes -- it does NOT assert that the described change is in effect. Prospective is not asserted." .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/horizon#LegislativeCandidateChange> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/horizon> .
